{
  "stem": "14091.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And I would run to Lapuszyno, to Celia, that I must promise her.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "But those were her last words.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "She just died.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [SIGHS] I-- I-- I was kneeled down near her.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And I wanted really to keep the promise.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "When I got up, I wanted to start running, and I was shot.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "I was shot in my leg.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And I saw it was torn out, and the blood would start running.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And also, it was scratched, my head.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And my head-- and my head start bleeding.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And my-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] my hair.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] When I was-- I ran for a little bit.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "But I felt I couldn't.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "I returned to my mother.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And I just lay on the top of her.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The days were short, because it was late in fall.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "It was very cold, almost freezing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] When the shooting subsided, and they did a marvelous job.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "Because from this ghetto, you wouldn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "Only I and one more person survived.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] [SIGHS] What they did, they went-- they came with lots of wagons and sleds.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And they collected the dead people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] They collected, they threw us in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "I-- intended-- I played dead.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "And they would-- two people would just throw the dead people in the wagons and some other means.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "They brought us to big pit, which it was very large.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "It was open.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "And they start throwing the bodies in the pit.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It was quite-- it took several hours until they cleaned, and digged, and brought everybody dead.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "And they brought us in to the pit.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
